reviews.text:
Strongly recommend.
Fantastic place for group of friend. Hong Kong style local food. love it

Dining experience was ok, locals frequent this place. Servings was abit big though. We ordered four dishes for three people and we couldn’t finish. The fried calamari wasn’t fantastic but the claypot chicken was interesting.
Local restaurant. Apart from local cuisine, it also serves barbequed food. My recommendation is barbequed eggplant. Pricing is relatively cheap.
taken here by local friends. Good food, down to earth, serving locals rather than tourists.
Very nice food, good chef in cooking traditional Chinese food.
